#: ../contents/ui/configTextIconFix.qml
msgid ""
"Fix text and icon colors/font for widgets where the normal method doesn't work or is reset by the widget.<br> - <strong>Mask</strong>: Force color on SVG icons, useful for symbolic icons.<br> - <strong>Color Effect</strong>: Force color on text and icons using post-processing effect, useful for non-symbolic icons.<br> - <strong>Refresh</strong>: Re-apply color/font at a fixed interval, useful "
"for widgets that recreate or recolor content themselves.<br>To restore the <strong>Mask<strong> and <strong>Color Effect</strong> disable and restart Plasma or logout."
msgstr ""
"用於在一般的設定方式無效或是元件本身將其重設的情況下，修正元件文字和圖示的顏色/字型。，<br> - <strong>遮蔽</strong>：在 SVG 圖示上強制上色，適用於符號圖示。<br> - <strong>色彩效果</strong>：以後製效果對文字和圖示強制上色，適用於非符號圖示。<br> - <strong>重整</strong>: 以一個固定間隔時間重複套用顏色/字型，適用於元件會自行重建或是自行重新上色的情況。<br>若要還原 <strong>遮蔽</strong> 和 <strong>"
"色彩效果</strong> ，請移除設定後重新啟動 Plasma 或是登出。"

